{"tid":18334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"兩雙龜開唔到眼點算","createTime":"2016-12-02T08:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T14:19:45.000Z","uid":41801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6ebe96cf9873d39d4f8de885772321c5179bb83","tid":18334,"uid":41801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:36:58.000Z","msg":"課室養左兩隻巴西龜 <br />\n早幾日唔知係咪洗缸嗰陣俾梘液入眼<br />\n第日發現有一隻既左眼開唔到 仲紅左腫左<br />\n本身諗住洗下佢就無事 點知過多日就知奶野兩隻眼腫哂 仲有層白膜係上面完全開唔到隻眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網搵話係白眼症 用龜精靈會好 即刻買左枝黎滴眼 琴日滴完之後嗰陣係無事 今朝又腫返白返 仲搞到第二隻都有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫佢地滴完嗰下好似好痛咁 佢地係咁伸手想捽 好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地已經成個星期無食過野 仲係幼龜黎 會唔會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該點做佢地先會好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22989a6802da00789ee85b50e7b9433706409839","tid":18334,"uid":1315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:37:43.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"86a1e518acc681567646a471303d95bf2b6dbca1","tid":18334,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:37:57.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad14357f9927c6e0065e3e6b65a49b76f6914ba","tid":18334,"uid":41801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:00:15.000Z","msg":"唔想佢地有事啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335891b03fc710ac5245a8a8900fec7472bf31c8","tid":18334,"uid":41801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:01:16.000Z","msg":"負擔唔起帶龜睇醫生既錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa835fa5f6219ab5da773fd8f603492d25298788","tid":18334,"uid":41801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce3d9a982855e7aeb1386fdb3f8b35686805778","tid":18334,"uid":41801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:41:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87c61d72b5dc6a11ce21fb0bba4e0e5f0d72f5a","tid":18334,"uid":41801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30116e175f56cd629bbc5a209db4af883f80c73","tid":18334,"uid":14992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:47:56.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦 要幾錢左右？"},{"pid":"2dc1559ac7c88c286a3163d16bafc592d1ebe1c0","tid":18334,"uid":41801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:00:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇醫生啦 要幾錢左右？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問人話要過千同要book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d523929e5388a92c152cf81548bd8c68a8ec35d","tid":18334,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:02:20.000Z","msg":"全班夾錢唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3985d0db249a5888ac4448c9b9d5cf050d62d8ae","tid":18334,"uid":35749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:02:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇醫生啦 要幾錢左右？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問人話要過千同要book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問屋企人借 如果唔係死架喇 1個星期差不多了"},{"pid":"ac04e47cc23060dea7e9027df92316484637e369","tid":18334,"uid":36366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:18:54.000Z","msg":"我屋企隻龜細個嗰陣都有咁嘅情況<br />\n用龜精靈搞掂左<br />\n滴完之後要用龜精靈水浸住啲龜<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知仲點幫到你隻龜龜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb978df264aad312ccd7cb944243dafb979dff9","tid":18334,"uid":41801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:11:41.000Z","msg":"琴日滴左兩次龜精靈 今朝睇已經無再腫仲好精靈識單眼好生猛走黎走去 但仲係完全唔肯食野 蝦乾都唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38334a01931bb963069f98ae25a55bdef688e45c","tid":18334,"uid":28523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:19:45.000Z","msg":"土瓜環有個男醫生幾好，最近先帶左隻龜去睇。200蚊診金未計藥，建議你快d，尤其係幼龜，好脆弱。<br />\n冇記錯係叫土瓜灣動物醫院。"}]}